stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> idle

    idle --> drawing : startDrawing()
    note right of idle
        No click listeners on map.
        Cursor is default.
        User can browse the map freely.
    end note

    drawing --> idle : finishPolygon() [pointCount >= 3]
    drawing --> idle : resetAll()

    note right of drawing
        Cursor set to crosshair.
        Click listener adds markers.
        Double-click or first-marker click
        triggers finishPolygon().
    end note

    state drawing {
        [*] --> placing_points
        placing_points --> placing_points : map click (add marker, pointCount++)
        placing_points --> can_finish : pointCount >= 3

        can_finish --> can_finish : map click (add more markers)
        can_finish --> [*] : double-click or click first marker
    }
